msgid "Classroom Added Successfully! 🏫"
msgstr "¡Clase Añadida Correctamente! 🏫"

msgid "Classroom %(nameclass)s for course %(course)s has been created successfully."
msgstr "La clase %(nameclass)s para el curso %(course)s ha sido creada correctamente."

msgid "Student Deleted Successfully! 🗑️"
msgstr "¡Estudiante Eliminado Correctamente! 🗑️"

msgid "The student has been removed from the system."
msgstr "El estudiante ha sido eliminado del sistema."

msgid "Classroom Deleted Successfully! 🗑️"
msgstr "¡Clase Eliminada Correctamente! 🗑️"

msgid "The classroom has been removed from the system."
